# Error Bound

Suppose $\norm{\;f''(x)} \leq K$ for $a \leq x \leq b$. If $E_M$ is the error in the
Midpoint Rule, then $$ \norm{E_M} \leq \frac{K(b-a)^3}{24n^2}. $$

